humorous /ˈhjuːmərəs/

1. ADJ If someone or something is humorous , they are amusing, especially in a clever or witty way. 幽默的 

例： He was quite humorous, and I liked that about him. 他很幽默，我喜欢他这一点。 

2. humorously ADV 幽默地 

例： He looked at me humorously as he wrestled with the door. 他一边用力地开门，一边表情滑稽地看着我。

